channel.title: WWE's Greatest Moments
channel.desc: The WWE Championship is the richest prize any Superstar can attain. And in the 1990s, the competition for the coveted gold was at an all-time high. Relive the greatest battles of the decade for the WWE Championship, such as "Stone Cold" Steve Austin vs. The Rock, Bret "Hitman" Hart vs. Owen Hart, Shawn Michaels vs. Mick Foley, Hulk Hogan vs. the Ultimate Warrior and more!
